{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","symbolKind":"case","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."],"syntax":null}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contai